<br>
There will always be game mechanics that prevent true roleplaying in any game out there, from the paper and pencil to the MMORPG's.  It just can't be helped.  I don't want to cause any flame threads so I'll just leave it at this:<br>
<br>
If you feel that what the Defender's of Ak'Anon have planned is unfair (invoking Lag), then do not participate in the event.  But, I think that you will miss out on some excellent RP that day.  I know that Flippus doesn't plan on defending Ak'Anon with just Lag.. <br>
